---

---

<section
  class="relative pt-24 pb-32 bg-black"
  style="background-image: url('/soutlight-pictures-website/logo.png'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; background-size: 90%; background-attachment: fixed;"
>
  <!-- Overlay + blur su tutta la pagina -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.72); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 md:px-16 space-y-24">
    <!-- WHO WE ARE -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p
        class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-amber mb-6"
      >
        who we are
      </p>
      <h1
        class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-none mb-10"
      >
        SOUTHLIGHT PICTURES
      </h1>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          SouthLight Pictures is an American production company founded by Alex
          Caruso at the beginning of 2026. SouthLight Pictures aims to create
          compelling stories that push the boundaries of entertainment.
        </p>
        <p>
          We craft experiences that resonate with audiences around the globe.
          Alex Caruso believes in the power of narrative to inspire. With a
          commitment to quality and innovation, we constantly evolve and
          challenge the conventions of storytelling.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- THE FOUNDER -->
    <div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-16">
        <span
          class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-gray-500"
          >The Founder</span
        >
        <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/10"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0 items-start">
        <!-- Text -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:pr-16">
          <h2
            class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-2 leading-none"
          >
            Alex
          </h2>
          <h2
            class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-10 leading-none text-amber"
          >
            Caruso
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
            Alex Caruso's interest in film began as a child after he discovered
            the power of telling stories. When he moved to the United States as
            a teenager, he began directing horror short films, such as <em
              >Alone</em
            >, <em>The Shadow</em>, and <em>The Whistler</em>. Since then, he
            has written a horror TV show and feature movies.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mt-5">
            Selected to be one of the best first-time filmmakers in London and
            the best narrative short in Hollywood, Alex is now developing
            thriller and horror movies. His interest in the Catholic culture
            made him write and explore faith-based storytelling. Alex has built
            SouthLight Pictures into a production company dedicated to crafting
            unforgettable cinematic experiences that captivate audiences
            worldwide.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 mt-12 lg:mt-0 relative">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl">
            <img
              src="https://cdn.boldjourney.com/wp-content/uploads/In development/02/c-PersonalAlexCaruso__mefoto2_1706138798091.jpg"
              alt="Alex Caruso"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-0 w-16 h-1 bg-amber"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
